extends layout

block content
  section.info-card
    h1 About MysteryBox Market
    p MysteryBox Market is a fake e-commerce company created for our CSC 317 web development project.
    p Our idea is simple: customers choose a theme, purchase a box, and receive a surprise collection of small items related to that theme.
    p This website demonstrates products, search, accounts, a cart, checkout, and purchase history using Node.js, Express, and SQLite.
